---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';

/**
 * Terms draft (§6, Phase C7). Claims-safe lexicon: "as is, without
 * warranties" — the standard vocabulary that would trip lint:claims is
 * deliberately absent. Counsel review gates the final version.
 */
---

<LegalLayout
  heading="Terms of Use"
  title="Terms of Use | Needle Girlie"
  description="Terms of use for needlegirlie.com. Draft pending counsel review."
>
  <p>
    Welcome to needlegirlie.com, the website of Needle Girlie — the
    practice of Amy Palacios, FNP. By using this website, you accept
    these terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Information only</h2>
  <p>
    This website exists to describe the practice and its services and to
    route visitors to booking. Nothing on it is medical advice, and
    reading it does not create a provider–patient relationship with Amy
    Palacios, FNP. Clinical decisions happen in consultation, never on a
    website. If you are experiencing a medical emergency, call 911.
  </p>

  <h2>Booking happens elsewhere</h2>
  <p>
    Appointments are scheduled through Vagaro, a third-party service with
    its own terms. Needle Girlie does not operate Vagaro and is not
    responsible for it, or for any other external site this website
    links to.
  </p>

  <h2>Content and branding</h2>
  <p>
    The content, wordmark, and branding on this website belong to Needle
    Girlie and may not be reused without written permission.
  </p>

  <h2>No warranties</h2>
  <p>
    This website is provided as is, without warranties of any kind.
    Content may change or contain errors; Needle Girlie may update or
    remove any part of it at any time.
  </p>

  <h2>Governing law</h2>
  <p>
    These terms are governed by the laws of the State of North Carolina.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
